title: 648. 5 Takeaways from the Super Bowl, Kadarius Toney Joins & Remembering Chris Wesseling
itunes:title: 648. 5 Takeaways from the Super Bowl, Kadarius Toney Joins & Remembering Chris Wesseling
description:
Daniel Jeremiah, Bucky Brooks and Rhett Lewis look back at the weekend on a special new episode of Move the Sticks. To start off, the guys give their 5 takeaways from the Super Bowl between the Kansas City Chiefs and Tampa Bay Buccaneers (1:15). Next, Bucky talks to Florida wide receiver Kadarius Toney as he discusses who he models his game after, his passion for music and the draft process (22:34). To wrap up the show, the trio remember their friend and Around the NFL colleague Chris Wesseling (30:20). All that and more in this packed episode. Move the Sticks is a part of the NFL Podcasts Network.
